minesweeper

create a board of 9x9
create random number of bombs 

player choose a coordinate

x,y

([x-1,y] [x+1,y],[x+1,y+1],[x-1, y+1], [x-1,y-1],[x+1,y-1], [x,y+1] , [x,y-1]).count == zero

tiles has a readable value on count of adjacent bombs


run reveal on all surrounding coordinates

totleal - number of bombs  -= number of tiles revealed